<div id="mainpage">

<div id="overlay" style='display:none;'>
<script>
	if (localStorage && localStorage.getItem('mapmill:overlay') && location.hash != "#slideshow") {
		$('overlay').hide();
	} else { 
		$('overlay').show();
		localStorage.setItem('mapmill:overlay',true);
	}
</script>

<h2>Sort and select the best images to make a map</h2>
<p><i>It takes hours to go through the thousands of images we're capturing <a href="http://publiclaboratory.org/tool/balloon-mapping">from balloons and kites</a>, to pick out the best ones for inclusion in our <a href="http://grassrootsmapping.org/data">free and open source maps</a>. Help us by choosing the best images.</i></p>

<p>We want images that are aimed <b>straight down</b> and are <b>not blurry</b>. We also want images of as large an area as possible. The rest are not useful! If you're not sure, mark it OK. <a href="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1276/4703515530_4482bc2f15_o.png">Learn what makes a good image</a></p>
<p><i>Confused? Learn more about the project at <a href="http://grassrootsmapping.org">GrassrootsMapping.org</a>.</i></p>

<p>(Keyboard shortcuts: 1 = good, 2 = ok, 3 = not useful)</p>
<p><a class='button' href="javascript:void(0);" onClick="$('overlay').toggle()">close</a></p>
</div>


<% unless params[:style] == "embed" %><a target="_blank" href="/sites/<%= @image.site.name+"/"+@image.filename %>" id="expand">full resolution (<%= @image.hits %>)</a><% end %>

<div id="image">
<img src="/sites/<%= @image.site.name+"/"+@image.filename %>" />
</div>

<div id="buttons">
	<a class="green"  href="/vote/<%= @image.id %>/10/<%= @sitename %>">really good (1)</a>
	<a class="yellow" href="/vote/<%= @image.id %>/5/<%= @sitename %>">just ok (2)</a>
	<a href="/vote/<%= @image.id %>/0/<%= @sitename %>">not useful (3)</a>
</div>
<script>
shortcut.add("1",function() { window.location = "/vote/<%= @image.id %>/1/<%= @sitename %>" });
shortcut.add("2",function() { window.location = "/vote/<%= @image.id %>/5/<%= @sitename %>" });
shortcut.add("3",function() { window.location = "/vote/<%= @image.id %>/0/<%= @sitename %>" });

setInterval(function() {
	if (location.hash == "#slideshow") window.location.reload();
},10000)
</script>
</div>
